content.rendered:
About me

Rhonan Joined Regent Group in January 2020, having spent the last 4 and a half years working in the higher education sector. He has worked in multiple Student facing and departmental managerial roles and will brings knowledge and experience of Student Finance and Student Support to Regent. Rhonan also has experience in Training and Development, Project Management and the implementation of new policies and procedures and a background in the reconciliation of funding.

Key responsibilities

Overseeing and managing the Student Finance functions of Regent, offering student support and guidance whilst ensuring that SLC Minimum standards are adhered to. Rhonan plays a key role in working closely alongside our University partners to ensure that all students have funding in place, as well as a smooth collection of income from Student Finance.
